<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us - CoolSite</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
    }

    body {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* Navbar */
    header {
      background: #111827;
      padding: 20px 40px;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    header .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    header nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 25px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    header nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* About Section */
    main {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .about-box {
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .about-box h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-box p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4b5563;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background: #111827;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include("navbar") %>


  <!-- About Section -->
  <main>
    <div class="about-box">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>Welcome to <strong>CoolSite</strong> — a place where creativity meets technology. We are a small team passionate about crafting web experiences that are modern, user-friendly, and powerful.</p>
      <p>Founded in 2025, our goal has always been to help individuals and businesses bring their ideas to life on the web through smart design and clean code.</p>
      <p>Whether you're starting from scratch or improving something existing, we're here to help you every step of the way. Let’s build something amazing together.</p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include("footer") %>

</body>
</html>
